Text: BachelorBacheloretteHello everyone I hope youre all as excited as we are Were very anxious to see everyone We have pondered the idea of the BachelorBachelorette party and we both would rather have all our friends together rather than seperate So we hope you will all join us on Friday November th at PM Baker St BB Costa Mesa We will meet there then carpooltailgate to the Four Seasons Hotel in Newport Beach for an evening of drinks desserts and jazz Please reply and let us know youll be coming We hope to see everyone there Adnan Maylynn Do You Yahoo Yahoo GeoCities quick and easy web site hosting just month psinfo
